channel.title: God Wars?
channel.description:
Okay i'm a coder for this guy, and since day 1, he's been asking for a "God Wars Dungeon". I told him i'd try, but i honestly have no idea what he wants. He said something about the bosses and then you get god stuff. He said he's seen it in other sources, but he doesn't remember what ones. -.-
Can someone explain to me what it is, and give me a download link to a source that has one? I need to see what it is before i can add it to our server.
